IOC:

Inversion of Control means that spring can create objects in the form of beans.
There is no need to manually create object using new keyword
It creates bean in IOC container
This beans can be injected into a field of a class using @Autowire annotation.

Pre Condition is
-we need to tell java that i need to create the object of the respective class 
-For this we use annotations like @RestController | @Component | @Service


