Summary: Prototype
-If we Autowired prototype beans in singleton class then prototype beans acts as singleton it create while application run, not create in every hit
-If we Autowired prototype beans in prototype class then it not create on application run but it create beans every time when we hit or call that class
-If we Autowired singleton beans in prototype class then singleton bean create on application run but prototype class bean create every time when we call.